  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "chapterTitle": "第二章 视角",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_18_26647-27705",
          "range": "26647-27452",
          "rangeStart": 26647,
          "rangeEnd": 27452,
          "markText": "1)家庭社会经济地位(SES)属于低收入群体或较低阶层（例如父母职业为工人、体力劳动者或无业）[插图][插图];(2)来自农村的学生[插图][插图];(3)来自西部偏远地区的学生[插图];(4)第一代大学生，即父母双方均未受过高等教育的学生[插图]",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727227635,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-25 09:27:15",
          "chapterUid": 18,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=26647&rangeEnd=27452",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=26647&rangeEnd=27452"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "chapterTitle": "第六章 余论",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_17_11412-11491",
          "range": "11412-11491",
          "rangeStart": 11412,
          "rangeEnd": 11491,
          "markText": "布迪厄在《继承人》一书中说：“处于最不利地位的阶级……对于实现命运的途径过于不觉悟，从而促进了自己命运的实现，因而学校教育系统的合法性权威可以加剧社会不平等”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188208,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:08",
          "chapterUid": 17,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11412&rangeEnd=11491",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11412&rangeEnd=11491"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_17_19805-20684",
          "range": "19805-20239",
          "rangeStart": 19805,
          "rangeEnd": 20239,
          "markText": "随着习性不断地调和自身与场域之间的矛盾，一方面需要维持与旧系统的连贯性，另一方面又需要发展新的倾向以适应新环境，于是产生了布迪厄所预言的“习性裂化”[插图]p.511。一方面，寒门学子已经脱离原来生长的环境，接触了许多新鲜的观念和事物，与原本熟悉的自我逐渐拉开了差距；另一方面，其在名校新获得的身份和自我认知又不断被原先的自我和社会关系所干扰，以至于自我认同时刻处于一种不稳定或撕裂状态，个体因自己的出身陷入自卑感与羞耻感当中，甚至将自我分裂成多个部分[插图][插图]",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188207,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:07",
          "chapterUid": 17,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=19805&rangeEnd=20239",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=19805&rangeEnd=20239"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_17_24752-24813",
          "range": "24752-24813",
          "rangeStart": 24752,
          "rangeEnd": 24813,
          "markText": "我愿意跨出自己的舒适区，去挑战我习以为常的观念和生活方式，接受（至少是有反思性地拒绝）那些总是不假思索就拒绝的观念和事物。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188200,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:00",
          "chapterUid": 17,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=24752&rangeEnd=24813",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=24752&rangeEnd=24813"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第四章 努力",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_10_33117-33136",
          "range": "33117-33136",
          "rangeStart": 33117,
          "rangeEnd": 33136,
          "markText": "这种转变是从持续不断的社会性投入开始的",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188207,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:07",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=33117&rangeEnd=33136",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=33117&rangeEnd=33136"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_10_1514-1591",
          "range": "1514-1591",
          "rangeStart": 1514,
          "rangeEnd": 1591,
          "markText": "在这个问题上，大学生发展研究已经达成了一个基本的共识：学生必须主动投入，积极投身学校的各类教育实践，提升学习成果，主动与老师和同学互动，才更有可能取得成功",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188202,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:02",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1514&rangeEnd=1591",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1514&rangeEnd=1591"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_10_36241-36270",
          "range": "36241-36270",
          "rangeStart": 36241,
          "rangeEnd": 36270,
          "markText": "‘为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平’。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188202,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:02",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=36241&rangeEnd=36270",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=36241&rangeEnd=36270"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "chapterTitle": "第三章 家境",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_19_6835-6890",
          "range": "6835-6890",
          "rangeStart": 6835,
          "rangeEnd": 6890,
          "markText": "布迪厄在《继承人》一书中说：“处于最不利地位的阶级……对于实现命运的途径过于不觉悟，从而促进了自己命运的实现”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188206,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:06",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6835&rangeEnd=6890",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6835&rangeEnd=6890"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_19_20470-20537",
          "range": "20470-20537",
          "rangeStart": 20470,
          "rangeEnd": 20537,
          "markText": "优势阶层的父母插手少，可谓是一种“无为而治”。不过，尽管他们不会直接发表意见，却会为孩子提供足够的信息和资源，支持孩子做出明智的决定。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188204,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:04",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=20470&rangeEnd=20537",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=20470&rangeEnd=20537"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_19_8962-9039",
          "range": "8962-9039",
          "rangeStart": 8962,
          "rangeEnd": 9039,
          "markText": "即布迪厄所谓的“习性滞后”(habitus hysteresis)。“习性滞后恐怕是机遇和在抓住机遇所需的倾向之间存在差距的根据之一；该差距致使机遇被错过",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727188203,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-24 22:30:03",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060202&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=8962&rangeEnd=9039",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0032f50813ab7e04g012a8d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=8962&rangeEnd=9039"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "chapterTitle": "第五章 方向",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300060202_11_7638-7692",
